WEBVTT

00:01:57.085 --> 00:02:00.434
that all my training in architecture,
design and planning

00:02:00.458 --> 00:02:02.553
failed ground realities.

00:02:03.879 --> 00:02:07.497
And this is where I learned
the power of choice.

00:02:08.069 --> 00:02:10.044
I unlearned many things,

00:02:10.068 --> 00:02:11.908
but there are two myths about the poor

00:02:11.932 --> 00:02:14.625
that I would like to share
that we live with.

00:02:15.619 --> 00:02:17.643
The first myth is a perception

00:02:17.667 --> 00:02:21.095
that migration of poor people
into cities is a problem.

00:02:22.572 --> 00:02:24.904
Is migration really a choice?

00:02:25.831 --> 00:02:27.863
My mentor Sheela Patel

00:02:27.887 --> 00:02:31.410
asked to those who think
of this as a problem,